result.execSummary:
The defendant Englebert R. Auinger was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Englebert R. Auinger is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Englebert R. Auinger was found guilty of Hit and Run-Involve Injury, an unclassified felony, Wisconsin Statutes 346.67(1).
  • Englebert R. Auinger was found guilty of Cause Injury/Operate While und.Influence (1st) (PAC<0.15), an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 346.63(2)(a)1.
